# Base URL of the NestJS API (no path — the app appends /api/v1).
#
# Usually you can leave this UNSET in development: the app derives the host
# from the Metro bundler, which works on simulators AND physical devices as
# long as the API runs on the same machine as `expo start`.
#
# Set it explicitly to point elsewhere:
#   iOS simulator:     http://localhost:3000
#   Android emulator:  http://10.0.2.2:3000
#   Physical device:   http://<your-mac-LAN-IP>:3000
#   Staging:           https://staging-api.cleansource.sa
EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=
